agenda_items.name: 122016-ED&F-Mins; Apprvl 4 5/3/16
agenda_items.title:
Recommendation to approve the minutes of the Economic Development and Finance Committee meeting held Tuesday, 
May 3, 2016.

agenda_items.name: 122016-ED&F-R;&F; Econ Dev Initiatives Rpt
agenda_items.title: Recommendation to receive and file an oral report regarding the status of current economic development initiatives, strategies and/or plans including but not limited to the recent launch of BizPort, the Long Beach business portal website, and CityMart.

agenda_items.name: 122016-ED&F-R;&F; Bus & Econ Indicators
agenda_items.title: Recommendation to receive and file a report on business and economic indicators for Long Beach during the past two quarters, and concur with recommendation and/or provide direction to staff.

agenda_items.name: 050316-ED&F-HM; Repair Cover Plan
agenda_items.title: Recommendation to request City Manager to study, as approved by the City Council on August 11, 2015, whether the City of Long Beach should offer home repair coverage plans and/or warranties to residents through preferred partnerships or programs and determine the fiscal impact of any such potential options.
